	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, the SNES does absolutely not check it as it has no BIOS !
<br />However a game like Earthbound might do stuff like doing it's own CRC check and refuse to run normally if hacked. I don't think many other games did this though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

